item.title: Boat crash 2 men killed
item.description:
Boat crash 2 men killed
Boat crash at Key West Powerboat Races 2011. 2 men killed in powerboat crash, November 9, 2011 during the Super Boat International races Wednesday. I was a spectator watching the races, shooting from my phone. I catch the boat flip, so I posted originally on youtube as "Boat flip" because It was no crash, and no one died. AFTER 2 HOURS, THE LOCAL NEWSPAPER POSTED BREAKING NEWS: BOAT CRASH 2 MEN KILLED (Key West Citizen, keysnews.com), and people start commenting R.I.P., so I changed the name to what the newspaper said !!! I was shocked and extremely scared at that moment. Drivers got transported to the hospital, one died on the way, and the second after 2 hours in the hospital !!!....there is also a 8 min raw video of the crash scene for details ! After 2 days, on Friday, THIRD racer died in the hospital, after a boat flip. Condolences to their families !!! R.I.P
